Quickstrike:





Quickstrike crawled towards Stingtra. "Somethin' wrong?" he said. "No, ah 
don't need anything." He transformed to robot mode and looked around the 
interior. He sighed. "Ah gotta call fer boss-bot." He walked to the console 
and sat down. He opened up his comm-link to Megatron. "Boss, ah gotta talk 
t' Dark Mouse. Can ya send 'er back here?"
